Text: Fwd Your Quickencom CreditCheck Report is ReadyTradingpst Hey Click on the link below to view your most recent credit report THe membership is Password THere is alot of shit on there Try to sort through it we need to make it a goal to clean this up as best we can Im heading to the bank Love you Jo Original Message Follows From custserv ReplyTo To Subject Your Quickencom CreditCheck Report is Ready Date Tue May Dear Mr Williams The credit report you ordered from CreditCheck is now ready for you to view and download Simply come back to the CreditCheck web site Members Area exciteuaasp enter your membership and passcode numbers and viewdownload your report Please keep in mind that the Online Delivery feature we offer is compatible with the following web browsers Netscape Navigator or higher visit downloadindexhtml to upgrade Internet Explorer or higher on a machine running Windows or higher visit ie to upgrade AOL for Windows using Microsoft Internet Explorer or higher visit to upgrade If you are using Netscape Navigator or Internet Explorer or higher your browser must accept the cookie our server sends before it will allow you to view your report The cookie contains your membership and passcode number information and acts as a special pass allowing you to access specific areas of our web sitein this case your credit report Your browser will automatically accept the cookie unless you specifically tell it not to If you are using AOL you can confirm whether you have AOL for Windows by clicking on the Help link at the very top of the page then clicking on About America Online You should then see a box that has the AOL logo and the message America Online for Windows This version of AOL automatically comes with Microsoft Internet Explorer or higher You will be able to view or download your credit report for weeks after the date at the top of the report After that your report will be deleted Remember to print or save your report before exiting it so that you can refer to it later If you have any questions please call our CreditCheck Customer Service Center tollfree at Thank you Michael Gordon Vice President Customer Service CreditCheck ADCB QRptrdEq Get your FREE download of MSN Explorer at
